128
0:06:14.26,000 --> 0:06:17,000
So I said, "Please measure forever

129
0:06:17.26,000 --> 0:06:19,000
because in school they're teaching me

130
0:06:19.26,000 --> 0:06:22,000
that if I cannot measure it, it does not exist.

131
0:06:22.26,000 --> 0:06:25,000
It doesn't come into my frame of reference."

132
0:06:25.26,000 --> 0:06:27,000
So, how far does eternity go?

133
0:06:27.26,000 --> 0:06:29,000
What does forever mean?

134
0:06:29.26,000 --> 0:06:32,000
And I would lie there crying at night

135
0:06:32.26,000 --> 0:06:35,000
