152
0:07:16.26,000 --> 0:07:18,000
and get over this problem,

153
0:07:18.26,000 --> 0:07:21,000
and so I got over the problem.

154
0:07:21.26,000 --> 0:07:24,000
How did I do it? Tell a story.

155
0:07:24.26,000 --> 0:07:26,000
So what is a story?

156
0:07:26.26,000 --> 0:07:29,000
